  m_text: 'Use the WASD keys to control Tony Capelli (red).


    Use the space bar
    to interact with ladders.


    Hold right click to look around.


    Click
    the card at the bottom of the screen and then click where you want to place a
    piece of scaffolding in order to place scaffolding.


    Ladder scaffolds can''t
    be placed on top of each other.


    Don''t run out of scaffolding before you
    reach the top!


    Get to the top of the cavern to win.


'
